                    "company": "Wegener Media",
                    "description": "Innovation at Wegener Media is about creating new and sustainable businesses. Based on Wegener\u2019s core assets the team develops new products and services to the delight of our readers and partners. Our pipeline of ideas is continually filled in real-time, with both internal and external ideas. These ideas are based on authentic demand from the communities we serve and are validated based on insights and a continual learning method.\n\nIn the role of Innovation Consultant I focus on:\n\u2022 Identifying the best ideas and develop these into concepts, prototypes and pilots reaching new audiences and representing significant revenue potential by using an iterative approach to quickly develop and validate ideas.\n\u2022 Leading teams in the development of the idea by being involved in the strategy, concept, business model, validation and project management.\n\u2022 Bringing in my background in Content & Storytelling by being an in-house expert in that field, consulting with teams and working on productions together with them.\n\nAll Innovation Consultants at Wegener work on the concept and business development side of an idea while also bringing in all of their other background knowledge. We mostly work in fast-moving teams and have an hands-on attitude. \n\nWegener Media\u2019s history is based on 100+ years of strong connections with regional and local communities in the Netherlands. These relationships give us unique insights based on: Where They Live, What They Love and Who They Trust. Our brand of innovation uses a collaborative approach to solving the unmet and constantly evolving needs of the people within these communities.\n\nWegener Media is the largest cross-media publisher of regional and local news and information in the Netherlands. On a daily basis our print, digital initiatives and multi channel platforms reach millions of customers with news and information relevant to our communities in a way only Wegener can achieve.",
